text: Assia Uhanany (born 1987) is an Israeli deaf model and beauty pageant contestant. On 29 September 2018, she was crowned as the Miss Deaf World 2018 which was held in Prague, Czech Republic. She also became the first Israeli to win the Miss Deaf World contest. == References == Category:Living people Category:Israeli female models Category:Deaf beauty pageant contestants Category:Deaf people from Israel Category:Israeli beauty pageant winners Category:People from Tel Aviv Category:1987 births
